{"type":"article_comment","id":390860,"parentType":"article","parentId":19425,"uid":9304,"contents":"留头不留发，留发不留头<br>\n<br>\n《商君书》驭民五术：<br>\n<br>\n1愚民：统一思想。<br>\n<br>\n2弱民：国强民弱，治国之道，务在弱民。<br>\n<br>\n3疲民：为民寻事，疲于奔命，使民无瑕顾及他事。<br>\n<br>\n4辱民：一是无自尊自信；二是唆之相互检举揭发，终日生活于恐惧氛围中。<br>\n<br>\n5贫民：除了生活必须，剥夺余银余财（即通货膨胀或狂印钞票）；人穷志短。<br>\n<br>\n五者若不灵，杀之。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DZS__CUWkAAOfDK?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DZS__CUWkAAOfDK?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DZS__CUWkAAOfDK?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-05-27","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}